343
00:16:03,466 --> 00:16:05,966
-That's right, my boy.

344
00:16:06,066 --> 00:16:07,766
-Father, I would
like to introduce you

345
00:16:07,866 --> 00:16:09,833
to my fiance, Ranma Saotome.

346
00:16:09,933 --> 00:16:11,733
-What are you saying?

347
00:16:11,833 --> 00:16:12,933
-Oooh!

348
00:16:13,033 --> 00:16:14,733
